{"tid":2358721,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔行山都減到肥","createTime":"2021-01-08T10:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:18:02.000Z","uid":207727,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e66a5171c56f5235351bbe26f6c388b7e76d0b25","tid":2358721,"uid":207727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post有人講行山3個月減到10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又分享下自己1個月減5kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日lunch同啲同事淨係食譚仔<br />\n呢個同事食厭咗就揾另一個同事食<br />\n點都會有一個想食譚仔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後去到淨係叫竹笙米線清湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚就照以前咗食<br />\n零食完全唔食 <br />\n野飲就只飲水/茶/醋溝水<br />\n食足4個星期 +係屋企做15分鐘YouTube個啲workout <br />\n成功減到5kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果黎緊夜晚都食少啲飯<br />\n相信下個月會減多5kg 達到理常體重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟著只要日日都keep住食竹笙米線就可以keep住理常體重了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗行3個月山已經減到10kg了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有少少線條幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037d55c130eb7905977449fa4fab42ef1ecdb0e7","tid":2358721,"uid":20302,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣食法 <br />\n你就算減 都係脂肪 肌肉 水份 一齊減<br />\n分分鐘肌肉跌最多  <br />\n<br />\n睇數字有尻用  最後個身型仲柒"},{"pid":"b122d46384e8f67da1368771e1b9d1636398f963","tid":2358721,"uid":188374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"洗咩為飲食台D肥豬去開個post<br />\n佢地咁食法減乜鬼，注定失敗<br />\n飲食台有幾條友都係肥人黎"},{"pid":"f49ec146ffe7b8b0ef9f6bc11b695c7e374ee7d6","tid":2358721,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b122d46384e8f67da1368771e1b9d1636398f963","tid":2358721,"uid":188374,"like":3,